{
  "stem": "10.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 38.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he comes to the camp, and I give him the report, saw so many people-- one is missing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They knew already that one is missing because [PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] the fence was cut, and he escaped.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he could escape because this spot of the camp, on Sunday when all the people in the camp not going out to work, this was not occupied.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Only the fence was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He knew about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He did say escape on Sunday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He went through and disappeared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They never caught him, and we never knew what happened to him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But we think he made it to the Poles, in the mountains, but he was killed right away because he didn't speak Polish, only German.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They considered him as a spy and they killed him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Rudy Kahn.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a German-Jew and half-Jew, and no trace about him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After a while when the SS men reported that they found the missing one-- I mean, he is from the re-educational camp, the kapo, the block eldest.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was called to the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he asked me, said, Halbreich, you did not know that he escaped?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, no, you have to realize I'm only a week with him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we hardly communicated privately, only officially, what we have to do next day and what's happened and so far.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I read a book, and he read a book, and we fall asleep, this was all.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know him even.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I hardly knew him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was only one week I'm there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he tells me, from now on, you're taking over the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I became the camp oldest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And right away I sent-- I asked the hospital to send me a doctor because I cannot take anymore-- help the ambulance.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have to take care of the camp-- of the whole camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they sent me Dr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Winter, Alfred Winter from Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
